{"tid":1682433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【 DQ事件｜眾院外交委員會：參院請盡快表決《法案》】","createTime":"2019-10-30T04:57:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T10:12:50.000Z","uid":125168,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a47aba21de7de18a2ed73c71bc7ff037711d3c74","tid":1682433,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:57:08.000Z","msg":"【🇺🇸 DQ事件｜眾院外交委員會：參院請盡快表決《法案》】<br />\n<br />\nDQ引發的國會反響繼續燒，今次連眾議院外交事務委員會都出聲。<br />\n<br />\n委員會批評，決定誰人入閘參選的應該是香港人，而不是中共，直言北京一再破壞「一國兩制」的行為不能坐視不理。<br />\n<br />\n《法案》宜家卡喺參議院，但委員會就tag埋決定議程的參議院多數黨領袖Mitch McConnell，要求盡快表決《法案》。<br />\n<br />\n正如友台手足提醒，唔駛放負，多謝兼Tweet 爆佢已經好夠力<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HouseForeign/status/1189267453911674880\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHouseForeign%2Fstatus%2F1189267453911674880&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt351e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=22a02ce7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHouseForeign%2Fstatus%2F1189267453911674880&h=a287cba0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HouseForeign/status/1189267453911674880</a><br />\n<br />\n========<br />\n🗺【支持眾志國際連結眾籌】<br />\n讓香港人權民主法案遍地開花｜<a href=\"http://bit.ly/intlcrowdfunding\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fintlcrowdfunding&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt351e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=2f8d824f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/intlcrowdfunding</a><br />\n<br />\n『零時差』收取國際資訊 <br />\n👉 <a href=\"http://t.me/demosisto_Int\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdemosisto_Int&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt351e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=2b914959\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/demosisto_Int</a>"},{"pid":"1ccc07afc810bf29d47bcf098f3ab133ce5a465e","tid":1682433,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:57:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zSLXe8W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn